		"description": "Currently Hyperloop for Windows is highly coupled with Titanium SDK even after we modularize Hyperloop (TIMOB-24093). For instance, some Hyperloop-related code generation logic and templates are done in Titanium SDK. This situation is not ideal and we want to move all Hyperloop-related logic to Hyperloop module itself, that way we can update Hyperloop _without_ updating Titanium SDK.\r\n\r\nFor now I can find following parts that can be decoupled with Titanium SDK\r\n\r\n- TItaniumWindows_Hyperloop code generation\r\n- Hyperloop event handling code generation\r\n\r\nWe want to move these logic to Hyperloop plugin.\r\n",
